excluded loans that are 30days past due and still accruing, which are insured by u.s.
government agencies under the federal family education loan program of $942million, $824
million and $663million at december31, 2009, 2008 and 2007, respectively. these amounts are
excluded, as reimbursement is proceeding normally.
