expected credit losses for consumer prime residential mortgage, and student and certain other
securitizations are incorporated into other assumptions.
jpmorgan chases interest in securitized assets held at fair value
the following table summarizes the firms retained securitization interests, which are carried at
fair value on the firms consolidated balance sheets. the risk ratings are periodically reassessed
as information becomes available. as of december31, 2009 and 2008, 59% and 55%, respectively, of
the firms retained securitization interests, which are carried at fair value, were risk rated a
or better.
